00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:55.290
get to Christina
and your background,

00:02:55.290 --> 00:02:57.850
about the connection
there, with Two James.

00:02:57.850 --> 00:03:00.570
BRAD GREENHILL: So my
partner in the restaurant,

00:03:00.570 --> 00:03:05.720
Courtney, had this idea,
let's get a food truck.

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:08.400
And I was like, you know, OK.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:09.060
I guess so.

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:11.430
Why not?

00:03:11.430 --> 00:03:16.020
At the time, I was transitioning
out of doing web development

00:03:16.020 --> 00:03:19.650
and pretty much doing
pop-ups full-time.

00:03:19.650 --> 00:03:24.270
And I was actively working
on opening a restaurant,

00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:28.880
but nothing had really
materialized quite yet.

00:03:28.880 --> 00:03:31.710
And so we're like, yeah,
let's get the food truck.

00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:34.110
You know, she wanted it
because she did events,

00:03:34.110 --> 00:03:36.060
so she thought it
would be cool to be

00:03:36.060 --> 00:03:39.000
able to have a truck at
her events to serve food

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:39.510
or whatever.

00:03:39.510 --> 00:03:43.590
And I was just interested
in cooking all the time.

00:03:43.590 --> 00:03:47.430
So we bought a truck,
with the intention

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:50.130
of sort of setting
up in different spots

00:03:50.130 --> 00:03:51.350
all around town.

00:03:51.350 --> 00:03:55.020
But about a couple of
months after we bought it,

00:03:55.020 --> 00:03:56.760
it broke down.

00:03:56.760 --> 00:03:57.840
The axle broke.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:03.540
And so we were storing it
right next door to Two James,

00:04:03.540 --> 00:04:04.880
because that was the--

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:06.796
there was a restaurant
finally going in there,

00:04:06.796 --> 00:04:09.720
but that was the spot that I
was in talks with about possibly

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:11.040
opening a restaurant there.

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.220
And my good friends
had started Two James.

00:04:13.220 --> 00:04:16.660
So we had planned on
serving there already.

00:04:16.660 --> 00:04:18.959
And then we were
just stuck there

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:21.380
once we broke down, because
we didn't have the money

00:04:21.380 --> 00:04:23.190
to get it fixed.

00:04:23.190 --> 00:04:24.580
SPEAKER: That's awesome.

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:29.699
BRAD GREENHILL: Yeah, it was a
very, highly illegal operation.

00:04:29.699 --> 00:04:30.490
SPEAKER: Operation.

00:04:30.490 --> 00:04:32.486
BRAD GREENHILL: Yeah.

00:04:32.486 --> 00:04:36.840
