00:05:46.090 --> 00:05:48.167
like more stuff that
I would have never

00:05:48.167 --> 00:05:49.250
expected to have happened.

00:05:49.250 --> 00:05:49.770
And it's just--

00:05:49.770 --> 00:05:50.220
BRAD GREENHILL: Right.

00:05:50.220 --> 00:05:51.090
The truck was--

00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:51.780
CHRISTINA PONSARAN:
It's terrifying.

00:05:51.780 --> 00:05:52.655
BRAD GREENHILL: Yeah.

00:05:52.655 --> 00:05:56.750
The truck was a terrifyingly
awesome experience.

00:05:56.750 --> 00:05:59.670
What was kind of funny about it
